| 7 | Critical | `routes.js:666` | `console.err` does not exist — will throw on Supabase error in `/addOpinion` |
| 2 | Critical | `uploadController.js:76` | `throw` in catch block instead of `res.status()` — request hangs |
| 3 | Critical | `Api.js:665` | `!response` check instead of `!response.ok` — HTTP errors silently ignored |
| 1 | Important | `OnboardingWizard.jsx:96` + `ProfileSetupStep.jsx:65` | Profile save errors swallowed; wizard always advances even on failure |
| 9 | Important | `OnboardingWizard.jsx` + `ProfileSetupStep.jsx:69` | Taken username can be submitted; `isValid` does not block it |
| 4 | Important | `uploadService.js:44` | Username uniqueness check doesn't exclude current user — retry causes 409 |
| 6 | Important | `checkUserController.js:10` | Always returns 500; ignores `status: 400` thrown by service |
| 5 | Minor | `TypewriterText.jsx:21` | `onComplete` missing from `useEffect` deps — stale closure |

