 74→                    <path d="M3 17.25V21h3.75L17.81 9.94l-3.75-3.75L3 17.25zM20.71 7.04c.39-.39.39-1.02 0-1.41l-2.34-2.34a.9959.9959 0 0 0-1.41 0l-1.83 1.83 3.75 3.75 1.83-1.83z" />
